          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <node refid="T6" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T5" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1060</offset>
        <text>A global compilation also indicates that hotspots of silicon burial in the ocean are all characterized by high silica to organic carbon export ratios, a diagnostic trait for diatoms growing under iron stress.
</text>
        <annotation id="T7">
          <infon key="brat-id">T7</infon>
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
