          <node refid="T9" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1269</offset>
        <text>We therefore propose that prevailing conditions of silica limitation in the ocean are largely caused by iron deficiency imposing an indirect constraint on oceanic carbon uptake.
</text>
